# Force LF line endings in the working tree on every platform.  Several
# tests embed checked-in assets (the sample dcrd.conf, the differential
# vectors) with include_str!/include_bytes! and compare them byte for
# byte against dcrd-generated fixtures, so a CRLF checkout on Windows
# would corrupt those comparisons.  Git still auto-detects binary files
# and leaves them untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
